      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines an update to RFC 1354.  The significant difference between this MIB and RFC 1354 is the recognition (explicitly discussed but by consensus left to future work) that CIDR routes may have the same network number but different network masks. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
